target.value:
Continued technical assistance in support of increasing MCV2 uptake in Ethiopia in Oromia Region, including
 a) programmatic support for strategies to increase uptake;
 b) support for increasing the quality of recording/reporting of vaccines doses delivered in 2YL;
 c) assessing strategies for improving defaulter tracing and, use of MCV2 as an opportunity for catch-up of children who missed their measles vaccination during the first year of life; 
d) communications messaging to increase awareness and demand for MCV2; 
e) capacity building for data quality assurance, analysis and triangulation of MCV1 & MCV2 data, measles surveillance data and outbreak data at the district level); 
f) support field implementation of operations research on aforementioned topics

